scenes.description: Mori Calliope performs 'CROWN' with BOOGEY VOXX.
Mori Calliope and BOOGEY VOXX exchange goodbyes after their performance.
Mori Calliope reflects on her long-standing friendship with BOOGEY VOXX.
Mori Calliope announces and explains how to purchase her concert Blu-ray.
Mori Calliope reveals her 3D showcase merchandise: a pendant accessory set.
